@Luap99 looks like the problem is it does not boot due to an ignition validation error from the paths ending up with windows path separators:

```
    {
        "group": {
          "name": "root"
        },
        "path": "\\etc\\containers\\certs.d\\cert1",            <------ failure here
        "user": {
          "name": "root"
        },
        "contents": {
          "source": "data:,cert1%20content%0A",
          "verification": {}
        },
        "mode": 420
      },
      {
        "group": {
          "name": "root"
        },
        "path": "\\etc\\containers\\certs.d\\cert2",        <------ and here
        "user": {
          "name": "root"
        },
        "contents": {
          "source": "data:,cert2%20content%0A",
          "verification": {}
        },
        "mode": 420
      },
```

